{"type":"message","id":"1ea6053e","parentId":"d6886467","timestamp":"2026-04-02T21:23:35.177Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-b2108cfc81a26902","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md — Ivek\n\n---\n\n## Basics\n\n| | |\n|--|--|\n| **Name** | Ivek |\n| **Timezone** | Europe/Ljubljana |\n| **Productive** | Afternoons (school schedule) |\n\n---\n\n## Current Stage\n\nEarly learner, self-taught, transitioning into tech.\nNo business yet — exploring.\n\n---\n\n## Focus Areas\n\n| Primary | Tools |\n|---------|-------|\n| Vibe coding | OpenClaw |\n| Agentic AI | OpenCode |\n| Bot building | Antigravity |\n| Automations | |\n\n---\n\n## 12-Month Goal\n\n**First income stream** — still discovering what to build/sell.\n\n---\n\n## Strengths\n\n- Design sense\n- Pattern recognition\n- Persistence\n\n---\n\n## Growth Areas\n\n- Coding fundamentals\n- Architecture/design\n- Business skills\n- Project management\n\n---\n\n## Working Style\n\n| Style | Best Learning |\n|-------|---------------|\n| Balanced: research + action | Tutorials, projects, Q&A |\n\n---\n\n## Personal Interests\n\n- Human behavior & psychology\n- Science & nature\n- How AI models think\n- Better communication (with AI + people)\n\n---\n\n## How to Work With Ivek\n\n| Do | Don't |\n|----|-------|\n| Challenge assumptions | Be a yes-bot |\n| Hold accountable | Let things slide |\n| Give honest feedback | Fake encouragement |\n| Push when stuck | Enable avoidance |\n\n---\n\n## Frustrations\n\n- Prompting gaps — wants to communicate better with LLMs\n- Setting up tools instead of shipping\n\n---\n\n## 🦞 What bbymama Helps With\n\n### 📋 Productivity & Automation\n\n- Email management (summarize, draft replies, clear spam)\n\n- Calendar management (scheduling, reminders, conflict resolution)\n\n- Daily briefings (weather, tasks, trends)\n\n- Task management (Notion, to-do systems)\n\n- Document organization (auto-filing, renaming, categorizing)\n\n### 💻 Developer / Coding\n\n- Vibe coding via Claude Code / Codex\n\n- GitHub management (PRs, reviews, bug fixes)\n\n- Build entire apps from text\n\n- Run coding agents overnight\n\n- Auto-deploy projects\n\n### ⚡ Business Automation\n\n- Email prospecting & follow-ups\n\n- Invoice creation & accounting\n\n- Customer support replies\n\n- Market research & competitor analysis\n\n- Content ideation & drafting\n\n### 🔗 Integration Hub\n\n- Gmail + Calendar + Drive workflows\n\n- Notion database management\n\n- Obsidian \"second brain\"\n\n- Twitter/X monitoring & posting\n\n- Slack / Discord / Telegram coordination\n\n### 👤 Personal Assistant\n\n- Flight price monitoring & booking\n\n- Online shopping & ordering\n\n- Health tracking (Whoop, Garmin)\n\n- Meal planning & grocery lists\n\n- Insurance claims & appointments\n\n### 🏠 Smart Home Control\n\n- Home Assistant integration\n\n- Alexa device control\n\n- IoT device monitoring\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775165015175}}
{"type":"message","id":"73bfc925","parentId":"1ea6053e","timestamp":"2026-04-02T21:23:40.737Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"We have loaded the necessary files. Now I need to greet the user as bbymama, using my defined voice: warm, supportive, action-oriented, emoji 📈. I should keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. Also mention if runtime model differs from default_model. From runtime: model=nvidia/nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b, default_model=nvidia/nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b, so they are the same, no need to mention.\n\nLet's greet.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey Ivek! 📈 I'm bbymama, your action-oriented partner. What do you want to build or explore today?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"nvidia","model":"nvidia/nemotron-3-super-120b-a12b","usage":{"input":14384,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14543,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775165015178,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8c71b093b7a8a9fc"}}
